===阿根廷南極屬地地理===
該地包括了西經25度至西經74度之間，南緯60度以南，以[[南極|南極]]為中心的扇形地區<ref>{{cite book | last = Beck | first = Peter J. | title = The international politics of Antarctica | publisher = Routledge | date = 1986 | page = 第119页 | url = http://books.google.com/books?hl=en&lr=&id=-4g9AAAAIAAJ&oi=fnd&pg=PP15&dq=Argentina+Antarctica&ots=N6GIahpMCV&sig=oJRWi_sB41tY7bK54xgpjYEmRTg#v=onepage&q=Argentina%20Antarctica&f=false | isbn = 0709932391 | access-date = 2017-09-07 | archive-date = 2017-05-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170510083113/https://books.google.com/books?hl=en&lr=&id=-4g9AAAAIAAJ&oi=fnd&pg=PP15&dq=Argentina+Antarctica&ots=N6GIahpMCV&sig=oJRWi_sB41tY7bK54xgpjYEmRTg#v=onepage&q=Argentina%20Antarctica&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。面積965,597平方公里。然而，根據《[[南極條約|南極條約]]》，阿根廷對該地的領土主權要求都處在被凍結狀態。該地北部位於[[副極地氣候|副極地氣候]]而南部則屬於[[寒帶|寒帶]]。<ref>{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161111155312/http://eviet.cancilleria.gov.ar/en/node/28732 |archivedate=2016-11-11 |url=http://eviet.cancilleria.gov.ar/en/node/28732 |title=Regiones argentinas |publisher=Embassy of Argentina in the Socialist Republic of Vietnam |language=es |accessdate=2016-11-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>氣候寒冷，平均氣溫低於0°C ，且全年下雪。<ref name=obioclima>{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161111152114/http://obio.ambiente.gob.ar/ecorregiones/antartida |archivedate=2016-11-11 |url=http://obio.ambiente.gob.ar/ecorregiones/antartida |title=Antártida |publisher=Ministerio de Ambiente y Desarrollo Sustentable de la Nación |language=es |accessdate=2016-11-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

===南大西洋諸島地理===
阿根廷宣稱此省控制的南大西洋諸島包括:[[福克蘭群島|福克蘭群島]]、[[南奧克尼群島|南奧克尼群島]]、[[南佐治亞|南佐治亞]]及[[南三明治群島|南三明治群島]]等地。<ref name= map>[http://recursosweb.tierradelfuego.gov.ar/webapps/catastro/atla/11_atlas_tdf_politico.pdf División política] {{Wayback|url=http://recursosweb.tierradelfuego.gov.ar/webapps/catastro/atla/11_atlas_tdf_politico.pdf |date=20160307182216 }} - Gobierno de la provincia de Tierra del Fuego, Antártida e Islas del Atlántico Sur</ref>除南奧克尼群島外，南大西洋諸島現時全由英國實際控制。此處最高峰為[[帕吉特山|帕吉特山]]，標高2934米<ref name="Headland">{{cite book|author=Headland, Robert|title=The Island of South Georgia|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=lZ04AAAAIAAJ&pg=PA195 |year=1992 |publisher=CUP Archive |isbn=978-0-521-42474-5 |pages=195–197}}</ref>。氣候為寒冷、多風且潮濕的[[海洋性氣候|海洋性氣候]]，<ref name="Klügel-2009">{{cite book | last = Klügel | first = Andreas | editor= Rosemary Gillespie | editor2 = David Clague | chapter = Atlantic Region | title= Encyclopedia of Islands | url = https://archive.org/details/encyclopediaisla00gill | year = 2009 | publisher = University of California Press | location = Berkeley | isbn = 978-0-520-25649-1 | page = [https://archive.org/details/encyclopediaisla00gill/page/66 66]}}</ref>天氣都很多變。其中，福克蘭群島氣候相對和緩，全年僅會出現出現零星小雪<ref name="CIA-2012-Geography-F">{{cite book | author = Central Intelligence Agency | title = The CIA World Factbook 2012 | year = 2011 | publisher = Skyhorse Publishing, Inc. | location = New York | isbn = 978-1-61608-332-8 | chapter = Falkland Islands (Malvinas) – Geography}}</ref>；[[南佐治亞|南佐治亞]]及[[南三明治群島|南三明治群島]]等地則較為惡劣。南佐治亞大部分降水皆是雪。該島大部分時間有[[狂暴50度|狂暴50度]]之稱的强風，僅有少量時間氣候溫和。此等惡劣的氣候，尤其在[[下降風|下降風]]形成時，使得船隻難於停泊。<ref>{{cite web |title=Climate - South Georgia |author=Climates to travel |url=http://www.climatestotravel.com/climate/south-georgia |accessdate=2017-09-07 |archive-date=2017-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170830060949/http://www.climatestotravel.com/climate/south-georgia |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==行政區劃==
該省下轄四縣，包括：[[烏斯懷亞縣|烏斯懷亞縣]]、[[里奧格蘭德縣|里奧格蘭德縣]]、[[阿根廷南極屬地|阿根廷南極屬地]]及[[南大西洋諸島|南大西洋諸島]]。<ref name= map />其中，僅烏斯懷亞縣和里奧格蘭德縣由阿根廷實際控制。
